      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of BMW\u2019s S54-powered masterpiece. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, providing a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventive maintenance, including documented subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The suspension retains factory geometry with refreshed OEM bushings, while the exterior finish exhibits exceptional depth and clarity with all original VIN tags present. This is a collector-grade specimen with a fully documented service history and zero mechanical compromises.",
